  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Existing law establishes the California State University and provides for its administration by the Trustees of the California State University. Existing law requires the trustees to provide by rule for the government of their appointees and employees.\n\nThis bill would make nonsubstantive changes to that requirement."
    }
